Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Sulu National Regional Agricultural School in the Municipality of Bongao, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Tawi-Tawi National Regional Agricultural School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 199
An Act Changing the Name of the Sulu National Regional Agricultural School in the Municipality of Bongao, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Tawi-Tawi National Regional Agricultural School
Section 1. The name of the Sulu National Regional Agricultural School in the Municipality of Bongao, Province of Tawi-Tawi, is hereby changed to Tawi-Tawi National Regional Agricultural School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 16, 1982
